init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You then follow the progress of your life as a chipmunk.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You try to avoid predators and eat plenty of acorns.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watch him carry off your child.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After a few years, you are digging in an apple tree when an osprey arrives to snatch your second child.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You grab its wing with your teeth and hang on for dear life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bird flies away with you, scraping the ground.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are flying over a cliff, and you know that the bird is about to drop you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are about to fall to your death.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You release the bird's wing, tuck your head into your chest, and pull in your legs.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then you notice that a nearby hawk is also flying at the edge of the cliff.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You spread out your body and become a parachute.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You land safely on a branch, high above the water.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The hawk then begins to talk to you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You know," she continues, "I'm really glad that I was able to save you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're not sure what she means.
